items.name: case inner
items.desc: An operation that joins the rows of the data tables whose values match exactly.

items.name: case left
items.desc: An operation that is the union between an inner join and the remaining rows from the original data table.

items.name: case right
items.desc: An operation that is the union between an inner join and the remaining rows from the secondary data table.

items.name: case outer
items.desc: An operation that is the union between a left join and a right join.

items.name: var hashValue: Int
items.desc: The computed hash value of the joining operation.

items.name: func hash(into: inout Hasher)
items.desc: Hashes the essential components of the joining operation by feeding them into the given hasher.

items.name: static func == (MLDataTable.JoinType, MLDataTable.JoinType) -> Bool
items.desc: Compares whether two joining operations are equal.

items.name: static func != (MLDataTable.JoinType, MLDataTable.JoinType) -> Bool
items.desc: Compares whether two joining operations are not equal.
